column5: Hey guys, 4 days and counting. I am heading up on Friday - Can't wait! Anyway, if you've been up in the area, can you give a bug report? Are the mosquitos as bad up there as they are in Northern WI and the U.P.? Thanks!

Just got back from Ear Falls area. Bugs were not bad at all. It was so windy and cold the mosquitos were not a problem. A few nights we were out and the wind died down and they came out but they were not a problem at all.
Wooglin, We will be at Evergreen next week. Where will you be.
We'll be at evergreen too - hope the weather is decent.. (green crestliner) cw
Big Fish...We will be the two guys fishing with our wives. Driving a Black SUV. Hope to see you at Evergreen. Mike
We will be down in the Hudson area 6/26 - 7/2.
